== 個人生活 ==
維那勒斯之所以被命名為小牛（{{lang-en|Maverick}}），是因為他的父親是《[[捍衛戰士|捍衛戰士]]》電影的粉絲<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://news.webike.tw/2016/05/26/yamaha-racing%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%88%87-maverick-vinales%E7%B0%BD%E8%A8%822%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84/ |title=Yamaha Racing宣布與 Maverick Viñales簽訂2年合約|publisher=Webike摩托新聞 |access-date=2020-09-22 |archive-date=2021-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122191239/https://news.webike.tw/2016/05/26/yamaha-racing%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%88%87-maverick-vinales%E7%B0%BD%E8%A8%822%E5%B9%B4%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

馬維里克的堂弟為[[世界超級摩托車錦標賽|世界超級摩托車錦標賽]]{{link-en|SSP300組別|Supersport 300 World Championship}}選手{{link-de|迪恩·貝爾塔·維那勒斯|Dean Berta Viñales}}，迪恩於2021年9月因賽道事故逝世，得年15歲。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dean Berta Viñales, morto a Jerez il cugino di Maverick dopo l'incidente in gara|url=https://www.corriere.it/sport/21_settembre_25/incidente-dean-berta-vinales-cugino-maverick-jerez-ospedale-gravi-condizioni-3bbe21c8-1dfc-11ec-986c-623ce988a833.shtml|publisher=Corriere della Sera|date=2021-09-25|access-date=2021-09-25|archive-date=2021-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211122132244/https://www.corriere.it/sport/21_settembre_25/incidente-dean-berta-vinales-cugino-maverick-jerez-ospedale-gravi-condizioni-3bbe21c8-1dfc-11ec-986c-623ce988a833.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

